The Paladin






Paladins are the very picture of a holy knight,fighting for the cause of good in all aspects of his life. They share some of the power of a Cleric, and a good deal of the fighting ability of a Warrior, but have a few powers of their own.

Paladin Members

1. Edgare ~Human~

2. Barret ~Human~

3. Raeb ~Human~

4. Glendiran ~High Elf~

5. Viss Valien ~Dwarf of the 33rd Rank~

6. Elam ~Half Elf of the 23rd rank~

7. Troeus ~Human of the 20th rank~
